Name: Delicious Saurus Crackers
Desc: Crackers shaped like little Saurians. The enticing aroma of butter draws forth the delightful interplay between the Cacahuatl and Grainfruit, while the cute shapes make them truly hard to put down. In the end, even the crumbs that slipped through your fingers were not to be spared!
Effect: Restores 34% of Max HP and an additional 1,900 HP to the selected character.
